3.20	The_Night_of_the_Hunter_(novel)	The Night of the Hunter (novel)	The Night of the Hunter is a 1953 thriller novel by American author Davis Grubb. The book was a national bestseller and was voted a finalist for the 1955 National Book Award.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e3/NightOfTheHunter.JPG/220px-NightOfTheHunter.JPG
